1. If you have a text file at "\Workspace\example.txt", which Path class method
  would you use to only get the name of the file?
Ans: getFileName()

2. If you have a text file at "\Workspace\example.txt", which Path class method would you use to only get the name of the file?
Ans: None of these are true

3. Which two arguments does the Files class method newBufferedWriter() require?
Ans: target path and charset

4. Which SimpleFileVisitor class method is invoked when the files of a directory are visited?
Ans: visitFile()

5. What is the Files class method that walks a file tree?
Ans: walksFileTree()
